      • findAttributeValue

        PsiAnnotationMemberValue findAttributeValue(java.lang.String attributeName)
        Returns the value of the annotation element with the specified name.
        Parameters:
        attributeName - name of the annotation element for which the value is requested. If it isn't defined in annotation, the default value is returned.
        Returns:
        the element value, or null if the annotation does not contain a value for the element and the element has no default value.

      • findDeclaredAttributeValue

        PsiAnnotationMemberValue findDeclaredAttributeValue(java.lang.String attributeName)
        Returns the value of the annotation element with the specified name.
        Parameters:
        attributeName - name of the annotation element for which the value is requested, declared in this annotation.
        Returns:
        the element value, or null if the annotation does not contain a value for the element.
